(561, 12, '2017-03-28 20:46:45', '2017-03-28 20:46:45', '[spb_blank_spacer height=\"80\" width=\"1/1\" el_position=\"first last\"] [spb_row wrap_type=\"thin-width\" row_bg_type=\"color\" color_row_height=\"content-height\" bg_type=\"cover\" parallax_image_height=\"content-height\" parallax_image_movement=\"fixed\" parallax_image_speed=\"0.5\" parallax_video_height=\"window-height\" row_top_style=\"none\" row_bottom_style=\"none\" parallax_video_overlay=\"none\" row_overlay_opacity=\"0\" row_padding_vertical=\"0\" row_margin_vertical=\"0\" inner_column_height=\"col-natural\" row_animation=\"none\" row_animation_delay=\"0\" width=\"1/1\" el_position=\"first last\"] [spb_text_block animation=\"none\" animation_delay=\"0\" padding_vertical=\"0\" padding_horizontal=\"0\" width=\"1/1\" el_position=\"first last\"]\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">An initiative of the <a href=\"http://www.excelined.org/\">Foundation for Excellence in Education</a> (ExcelinEd), Know Your Florida School is the prototype online school report card of the national <a href=\"http://knowyourschoolproject.org/\">Know Your School Project.</a></h2>\n[/spb_text_block] [spb_socialsharing enable_email=\"no\" enable_facebook=\"yes\" enable_linkedin=\"no\" enable_twitter=\"yes\" width=\"1/1\" el_position=\"first last\"] [/spb_row] [spb_row wrap_type=\"thin-width\" row_bg_type=\"color\" color_row_height=\"content-height\" bg_type=\"cover\" parallax_image_height=\"content-height\" parallax_image_movement=\"fixed\" parallax_image_speed=\"0.5\" parallax_video_height=\"window-height\" row_top_style=\"none\" row_bottom_style=\"none\" parallax_video_overlay=\"none\" row_overlay_opacity=\"0\" row_padding_vertical=\"80\" row_margin_vertical=\"0\" inner_column_height=\"col-natural\" row_animation=\"none\" row_animation_delay=\"0\" width=\"1/1\" el_position=\"first last\"] [spb_text_block title=\"Data\" animation=\"none\" animation_delay=\"0\" padding_vertical=\"0\" padding_horizontal=\"0\" width=\"1/1\" el_position=\"first last\"]\n\nThe focus of Know Your Florida School is unpacking the Florida Department of Education\'s annual Florida School Grades data to provide you and your community with important and actionable information about schools. All of the data you see on Know Your Florida School is from the reports and information publicly provided by <a href=\"http://www.fldoe.org/about-us/division-of-accountability-research-me.stml\">DOE’s Division of Accountability, Research, and Measurement</a>. Schools and school districts collect this information and provide it to the state throughout the year.\n\nThe majority of data currently available comes from DOE\'s 2015-16 School Grades report found on <a href=\"http://schoolgrades.fldoe.org/\">schoolgrades.fldoe.org</a>. The data is loaded directly from DOE reports into an API database maintained by Jacksonville Public Education Fund. No calculations have been performed on the data that powers Know Your Florida School.\n\nKnow Your Florida School will be expanding over the next year to include additional data and functionality. <a href=\"#signup\">Sign up to receive updates</a> when new features are made available.\n\n[/spb_text_block] [/spb_row] [spb_row wrap_type=\"thin-width\" row_bg_type=\"color\" row_bg_color=\"#00a7b9\" color_row_height=\"content-height\" bg_type=\"cover\" parallax_image_height=\"content-height\" parallax_image_movement=\"fixed\" parallax_image_speed=\"0.5\" parallax_video_height=\"window-height\" row_top_style=\"none\" row_bottom_style=\"none\" parallax_video_overlay=\"none\" row_overlay_opacity=\"0\" row_padding_vertical=\"0\" row_margin_vertical=\"0\" inner_column_height=\"col-natural\" row_animation=\"none\" row_animation_delay=\"0\" row_id=\"grade-calc\" width=\"1/1\" el_position=\"first last\"] [spb_column width=\"1/2\" el_position=\"first\"] [spb_text_block animation=\"none\" animation_delay=\"0\" padding_vertical=\"0\" padding_horizontal=\"0\" el_class=\"white-text\" width=\"1/1\" el_position=\"first last\"]\n<h3>Understanding School Grades</h3>\n<h6>School grades provide a clear way for the State of Florida to measure school performance.</h6>\n[/spb_text_block] [spb_button button_size=\"standard\" button_colour=\"white-purple\" button_align=\"align-left\" button_text=\"How Are School Grades Calculated?\" button_link=\"http://eeflrc.wpengine.com/about/school-grades/\" button_target=\"_self\" animation=\"none\" animation_delay=\"0\" width=\"1/1\" el_position=\"first last\"] [/spb_column] [spb_image image=\"125\" image_size=\"full\" image_width=\"400\" lightbox=\"no\" link_target=\"_self\" caption_pos=\"hover\" intro_animation=\"none\" animation_delay=\"200\" width=\"1/2\" el_position=\"last\"] [/spb_row] [spb_row wrap_type=\"thin-width\" row_bg_type=\"color\" color_row_height=\"content-height\" bg_type=\"cover\" parallax_image_height=\"content-height\" parallax_image_movement=\"fixed\" parallax_image_speed=\"0.5\" parallax_video_height=\"window-height\" row_top_style=\"none\" row_bottom_style=\"none\" parallax_video_overlay=\"none\" row_overlay_opacity=\"0\" row_padding_vertical=\"100\" row_margin_vertical=\"0\" inner_column_height=\"col-natural\" row_animation=\"none\" row_animation_delay=\"0\" width=\"1/1\" el_position=\"first last\"] [spb_text_block title=\"Project Team\" animation=\"none\" animation_delay=\"0\" padding_vertical=\"0\" padding_horizontal=\"0\" width=\"1/1\" el_position=\"first last\"]\n\nLed by ExcelinEd, Know Your Florida School is a result of a close partnership with Collaborative Communications Group, Social Driver and Jacksonville Public Education Fund (JaxPEF) with input and support from numerous stakeholders, partners and most importantly, parents.\n\n<a href=\"http://collaborativecommunications.com/\">Collaborative Communications Group</a> and <a href=\"http://socialdriver.com/\">Social Driver</a> are the winning design team from ExcelinEd’s 2015 My School Information Design Challenge to bring creative ideas to improving school report cards and information.\n\nJaxPEF is a Florida nonprofit that uses research to support high-quality public schools for all children in Duval County. They have been providing the greater Jacksonville community with easy access to information about their local schools since 2012 via School Facts Jax. In addition to providing valuable insight on parent and community use of school information, JaxPEF maintains the API database with the raw data that powers Know Your Florida School. For questions about the API contact JaxPEF at <a href=\"http://www.jaxpef.org/\">JaxPEF.org.</a>\n\n[/spb_text_block] [spb_image image=\"72\" image_size=\"full\" image_width=\"175\" lightbox=\"no\" link_target=\"_self\" caption_pos=\"hover\" intro_animation=\"none\" animation_delay=\"200\" width=\"1/4\" el_position=\"first\"] [spb_image image=\"71\" image_size=\"full\" image_width=\"175\" lightbox=\"no\" link_target=\"_self\" caption_pos=\"hover\" intro_animation=\"none\" animation_delay=\"200\" width=\"1/4\"] [spb_image image=\"74\" image_size=\"full\" image_width=\"175\" lightbox=\"no\" link_target=\"_self\" caption_pos=\"hover\" intro_animation=\"none\" animation_delay=\"200\" width=\"1/4\"] [spb_image image=\"73\" image_size=\"full\" image_width=\"175\" lightbox=\"no\" link_target=\"_self\" caption_pos=\"hover\" intro_animation=\"none\" animation_delay=\"200\" width=\"1/4\" el_position=\"last\"] [/spb_row] [spb_row wrap_type=\"thin-width\" row_bg_type=\"color\" row_bg_color=\"#00a7b9\" color_row_height=\"content-height\" bg_type=\"cover\" parallax_image_height=\"content-height\" parallax_image_movement=\"fixed\" parallax_image_speed=\"0.5\" parallax_video_height=\"window-height\" row_top_style=\"none\" row_bottom_style=\"none\" parallax_video_overlay=\"none\" row_overlay_opacity=\"0\" row_padding_vertical=\"60\" row_margin_vertical=\"0\" inner_column_height=\"col-natural\" row_animation=\"none\" row_animation_delay=\"0\" width=\"1/1\" el_position=\"first last\"] [spb_text_block animation=\"none\" animation_delay=\"0\" padding_vertical=\"0\" padding_horizontal=\"0\" el_class=\"white-text\" width=\"1/2\" el_position=\"first\"]\n<h6>View a list of frequently asked questions and answers on our FAQ page:</h6>\n[/spb_text_block] [spb_button button_size=\"standard\" button_colour=\"white-purple\" button_align=\"align-center\" button_text=\"Frequently asked questions\" button_link=\"/about/faqs/\" button_target=\"_self\" animation=\"none\" animation_delay=\"0\" width=\"1/2\" el_position=\"last\"] [/spb_row] [spb_row wrap_type=\"thin-width\" row_bg_type=\"color\" color_row_height=\"content-height\" bg_type=\"cover\" parallax=\"no\" parallax_image_height=\"content-height\" parallax_image_movement=\"fixed\" parallax_image_speed=\"0.5\" parallax_video_height=\"window-height\" row_top_style=\"none\" row_bottom_style=\"none\" parallax_video_overlay=\"none\" row_overlay_opacity=\"0\" row_padding_vertical=\"80\" row_margin_vertical=\"0\" inner_column_height=\"col-natural\" row_animation=\"none\" row_animation_delay=\"0\" row_id=\"center-heading\" width=\"1/1\" el_position=\"first last\"] [spb_text_block title=\"Know Your School Project\" animation=\"none\" animation_delay=\"0\" padding_vertical=\"0\" padding_horizontal=\"0\" width=\"1/1\" el_position=\"first last\"]\n\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-33 aligncenter\" src=\"https://eeflrc.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/logo-300x95.png\" alt=\"logo\" width=\"300\" height=\"95\" />\n\nParents expect a cutting-edge and user-friendly school report card tool, and ExcelinEd’s Know Your School Project is here to help states make that a reality.\n\nKnow Your Florida School is the live prototype for Know Your School, the national project promoting the transparency of school performance data. Together, the two serve as an innovative resource for states across the nation by exemplifying best practices and strategies for making school information and data understandable and useful for parents and community members.\n\nThe Know Your School Project shares detailed documentation of the processes and challenges associated with the data, technology, content and engagement with stakeholders that are essential to such an endeavor. All resources, as well as the open source code used to build Know Your Florida School, is freely available to other states to use as they build their own 21st century school accountability report cards.\n\n[/spb_text_block] [spb_video link=\"https://vimeo.com/191520535/d66562f1e7\" full_width=\"no\" width=\"1/1\" el_position=\"first last\"] [spb_blank_spacer height=\"60\" width=\"1/1\" el_position=\"first last\"] [spb_button button_size=\"standard\" button_colour=\"purple\" button_align=\"align-center\" button_text=\"Resources for SEAs\" button_link=\"http://localhost:8888/about/resources/\" button_target=\"_self\" animation=\"none\" animation_delay=\"0\" width=\"1/1\" el_position=\"first last\"] [/spb_row]', 'About', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '49-autosave-v1', '', '', '2017-03-28 20:46:45', '2017-03-28 20:46:45', '', 49, 'http://localhost:8888/49-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
